template<class U1, class U2> constexpr explicit([[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]) pair(const pair<U1, U2>& p);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`is_constructible_v<first_type, const U1&>] is [`true] and
[:zh_CN] [`is_constructible_v<first_type, const U1&>] 为 [`true] 并且
[item]
[:en] [`is_constructible_v<second_type, const U2&>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`is_constructible_v<second_type, const U2&>] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes members from the corresponding members of the argument.
[:zh_CN] 以实参的对应成员初始化其各成员。

[para:remarks]
[:en] The expression inside [`:key explicit] is equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] [`:key explicit] 中的表达式等价于：
[codeblock]
!is_convertible_v<const U1&, first_type> || !is_convertible_v<const U2&, second_type>
[codeblock:end]
[div:end]

