[:zh_CN] 赋值 [`p.first] 给 [`first]，并赋值 [`p.second] 给 [`second]。

[para:returns]
[:en] [`*this].
[:zh_CN] [`*this]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member operator=[!pair]]
[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr pair& operator=(pair&& p) noexcept([[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`is_move_assignable_v<first_type>] is [`true] and
[:zh_CN] [`is_move_assignable_v<first_type>] 为 [`true] 并且
[item]
[:en] [`is_move_assignable_v<second_type>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`is_move_assignable_v<second_type>] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:effects]
[:en] Assigns to [`first] with [`std::forward<first_type>(p.first)] and to
[`second] with [`std::forward<second_type>(p.second)].
[:zh_CN] 以 [`std::forward<first_type>(p.first)] 对 [`first] 赋值，并以
[`std::forward<second_type>(p.second)] 对 [`second] 赋值。

[para:returns]
[:en] [`*this].
[:zh_CN] [`*this]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] The exception specification is equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 其异常说明等价于：
[codeblock]
is_nothrow_move_assignable_v<T1> && is_nothrow_move_assignable_v<T2>
[codeblock:end]
[div:end]

